{"tid":1148754,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一厘低息，50萬元槓400萬元買美國國債","createTime":"2019-05-10T16:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:34:16.000Z","uid":58287,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c103c9991618e374ad1de5fbdcae23efb10e995c","tid":1148754,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190505/59555665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F59555665&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYFDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=90adb238\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F59555665&h=60fc9f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190505/59555665</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>從事金融業的妹妹接過咪來就解釋：「佢一直都將人工一半用來投資，2015年開始就每個月畀約3萬啦。點滾存呢，就唔係月供股票或基金，個啲收費貴。我哋就度咗個投資組合，入面有股票及債券，債券就儲夠一筆錢用槓桿方式去買，債券都係評級高嘅，其中就儲夠<strong>50萬元去槓400萬元嘅美國國債</strong>。」她補充，股票組合當中包括2016年騰訊（700）股價200元時買入50萬元，持貨2年去年股價突破400元時沽出，賬面賺約50萬元。</em><br />\n<br />\n睇到下面有D評論話因為美國國債低風險，所以有行可以用一厘低息借錢買槓大7倍，大家有無玩過？聽落唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dcf11142375931958868ca903a0891974dbd18","tid":1148754,"uid":19898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"人工一半 <br />\n每個月約俾3萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30cf236b25b59ebd7eeccc89431f76ff43bce42","tid":1148754,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"鍵融雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb327dbbab967585ae41d89e44640b86c9963906","tid":1148754,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20